- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category as the paper deals with ensemble learning, a subfield of machine learning.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is a possible category as the paper may involve visualizations of data and models in the context of image classification tasks.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with the development of a workflow for combining and manipulating classifier models, which is a topic related to AI.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of classifier models for document classification or information retrieval tasks.
